OL,7,FShe told ITV News Meridian: "We have
OL,8,Fnowhere that we can get together as a
OL,9,Ffamily. We can't sit and eat a meal
OL,10,Ftogether, which we're so used to doing.
OL,12,F"I've got a 15-year-old son who's
OL,13,Fautistic. He needs to have his own
OL,14,Fsafe space and his own area and he
OL,15,Fdoesn't have that.
OL,17,F"My mental health has been relatively
OL,18,Fstable for quite a long time. But this
OL,19,Fsituation has put my mental health on
OL,20,Fa downward spiral."
