OL,7,FKelly, her husband, son and two
OL,8,Fdaughters were made homeless when
OL,9,Ftheir previous private landlord
OL,10,Fdecided to sell the property.
OL,12,FThey have been told they could be
OL,13,Fwaiting as long as seven years for
OL,14,Fpermanent social housing.
OL,16,FKelly travelled to the Houses of
OL,17,FParliament on Thursday 24 October to
OL,18,Fwatch a debate on the issue of
OL,19,Ftemporary accommodation, called by her
OL,20,Flocal MP.
