OL,7,F"So, I'm calling for this government
OL,8,Fto step up and act to support local
OL,9,Fpeople out of homelessness and to
OL,10,Fsupport the council to support them."
OL,12,FHousing Minister Rushanara Ali told
OL,13,Fthe House of Commons: "This government
OL,14,Fis absolutely committed to addressing
OL,15,Fthe current high levels of
OL,16,Fhomelessness and rough sleeping and of
OL,17,Fcourse the barriers facing those who
OL,18,Fare in temporary accommodation that
OL,19,Fneed to have a home to live in that is
OL,20,Fsafe and secure."
